title: [Bloodriven Village, Blot Alley]
description: Chipped cobblestones scattered along the alley conspire with the street's acclivity, challenging pedestrians to pass through with ankles untwisted.  A dusty pile of crumbled brick and mortar lies beneath a chipped-up section of the eastern brick wall.

Slush-covered cobblestones scattered along the alley conspire with the street's acclivity, challenging pedestrians to pass through with ankles untwisted.  An unidentifiable pile of material lies beneath a chipped-up section of the eastern brick wall, covered in a thick layer of snow.
